>## [Author's Notice]($block.attrs('warning'))
> This Documentation is [incomplete](https://github.com/zigtools/www.zigtools.org/issues/1).

1. Install [Doom Emacs](https://github.com/doomemacs/doomemacs)
2. Enable `:tools lsp` module
3. Enable `:lang (zig +lsp)` module
4. Run `doom sync` in a terminal
5. Set in-editor configuration (optional)
6. Run `doom doctor` to check if Zig and ZLS have been found

## Configuration

Doom Emacs uses [lsp-mode](https://github.com/emacs-lsp/lsp-mode/) as the LSP Plugin. In-Editor configuration for lsp-mode can be found [here](/zls/editors/emacs).
